  "instructions": [
    "Roast the peanuts in a 350 degree oven for 10 minutes, or until fragrant.",
    "In a large copper pot, heat the sesame oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion, carrots, and celery, and cook until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Add the sliced mushrooms and cook until they release their moisture.",
    "Pour in the dashi broth and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Stir in the roasted peanuts and soy sauce.",
    "Serve the ozoni hot, garnished with chopped scallions if desired."
